Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cell can efficiently generate electricity using methane fuel; however, methane cracking at high temperature often results in carbon deposition that leads to degradation of power output.
Titulo: High performance, coking-resistant and sulfur-tolerant anode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Here, metal-oxide interface is in stiu constructed in LSCM anode to enhance methane oxidation.
Titulo: High performance, coking-resistant and sulfur-tolerant anode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The anchored interface demonstrated exceptionally high resistance to carbon coking and sulfur poisoning.
Titulo: High performance, coking-resistant and sulfur-tolerant anode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The peak power density with Cu0.5Fe0.5-LSCM anode is as high as 0.64 W cm(-2 )using methane fuel at 850 degrees C. Electrochemical measurement shows a stable power output under current density of 0.4 A cm(-2) using methane fuel even after 10 redox cycles at 850 degrees C.
Titulo: High performance, coking-resistant and sulfur-tolerant anode for solid oxide fuel cell
